Vedviroit yogoneant zonaurank martale. Zoinamni ani boudhdamni zonauranche hotyeadd cholloull ubaroli ani bhouxik lokanchem mot zonauranche hotyeadd bodl'le. Tori voidik dhormache khor vangddi brahmonn ani kxotriy hanni mat zonaurank marpachem soddlem na. Mohabharotachea kalla meren himsok yogone zatalech. Mohabharotachea kalla uprant jen'na boudhd ani zoinacho paddavo korun ary dhorm' voir sorlo ten'na porakromi kxotriy razamni oxvomedh yogone kel'leachem dakhle mellttat. Punn voixnnou dhormachea bhorbhorattichea kallant lokanche hea yogoneachea vaitt ani bhirankull chalivixim mot bodl'le.

Gitentlea goneanolkxonnant ohimsecho aspavo asa ani ohimsa mhollear xaririk top axil'leachem-i tatunt mhollam. Xrikrixnnachea kallant yogone yagachem borench bollgem axil'lem. Xrikrixnnachea kallantleanoch himsok yogonea add lokanchem mot lhou lhou korun bodlunk laglem.

Hindu somskritayentoli ohimsechi suvat spoxtt asa. Voidik dhormant dhormik mhotv axil'lea yogoneant zori zonauranchi hotea korpachi chal axil'li tori kallantoran he yogone bond poddle ani bhokti margacher adarit mokxomarg ruddh zalo. Ohimsa, soty ani brohmochry him totvam hindu dhormachim khaxelim angam zalim.

Mohatma gandhi chalu kallantolo ohimsecho ek vhodd upasok. Tannem soteagrohachem ek novem totv upegant haddlem ani taka adar mhunn ohimsek mhotv dilem. Achary vinoba bhave ho ohimsecho dusro vhodd upasok. Tachea motan nirbhoita, mog ani sohkary oxe ohimseche tin orth asat.

Ohimse vixim ostonti vicharountanchi vicharosoronni veglli asa. Amcheant dhorm' ani ahar hatunt jitlo lagosl'lo sombond asa titlo tanchea vicharount ani dhormik lokant to disna. Mams bhokxonn kelem va soro pielo mhunn te ostonti lokanchea dhorma add zaunk xokna.

Monxacho sobhavo songhrxoxil axil'lean taka svotachi ani svotache aspotichi rakhonn korche khatir zhujchench poddtta. Hem motint ghet zalear ohimsa totv apnnaunk sompe nhoi.Punn dusre votten svota jieuchem ani vangddach dusreankuy dieuche khatir palou divcho oxem mot apnnailear ahimsechem mhotv zannouta.

